{
  "stem": "21582.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Even that has, has, has, has moments that glow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "After that, things got much, much, dimmer, much, much worse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember the Germans marching in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was like a human, enormous machine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They wore leather-- you, you, you, you forget-- I-- they, they didn't even seem human because their faces were so immobile, so rigid.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So-- it's as though-- there, there, there was not a flicker of what I associate with a human face-- a blink, a smile, nothing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They just marched, helmets and leather and, and, and guns and bayonets and boots.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we-- the, the, the rasping, the beating of the march on, on, on, on the cobblestones, it just rang.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It just rang.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It, it, it just was like-- it, it filled the air.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It just filled the air.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And, of course, for us, we didn't know-- we didn't know what to expect.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I, as a child-- it was just overwhelmed by the fear, by, by, by, by the, I guess, inhumanity of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It just, just, just did not match with the world that I have known.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They marched in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And, of course, then the-- of course, you didn't realize that the Germans were not stationed in the areas where we lived.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They were pretty much-- I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But they were outside where, where, where we lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But they did come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They came in always unexpectedly, deliberately because they did want to catch us off guard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "One of the first things that I recall is confiscations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We had to surrender all the gold, wedding bands, and, and, and everything of value.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
